    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market. This vehicle remains in showroom-state, exhibiting an uncompromising level of care both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects a commitment to preservation, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. For the discerning individual who accepts only the finest, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
