    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-tier shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
