      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1988 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2, featuring the highly sought-after Getrag G50 5-speed transaxle with a factory limited-slip differential. This example remains mechanically peerless, powered by its original air-cooled 3.2L flat-six utilizing Bosch Motronic fuel injection. Recent comprehensive servicing includes a top-end refresh, valve adjustment, and a leak-down test showing less than 3% variance across all cylinders. The chassis remains structurally flawless with factory-spec torsion bars and Bilstein dampers. The exterior retains its original zinc-coated panels with consistent paint meter readings throughout. Rolling on staggered 16-inch Fuchs alloy wheels wrapped in N-rated Continental rubber, this 911 offers the visceral, analog feedback expected of a true survivor. Documentation includes a stamped service booklet and a detailed CoA.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Clean title. Garage kept. Smoke-free interior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, complemented by pristine wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every switch, dial, and digital display operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of every service record from day one. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic.",
      "price": 48500.0,
