      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! It's in stunning, like-new condition and has been pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, you won't find a scratch on it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty. It\u2019s a total dream to drive, so come check it out before it\u2019s gone!",
